{"tid":2005281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍備忘錄稱確診武漢肺炎者將終身失去美軍服役資格","createTime":"2020-05-07T04:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T04:33:21.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5aa5822aceb3981dadcda02ac00298c7830e80","tid":2005281,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國的武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒疾病，COVID-19）疫情嚴峻，目前全美已有122萬多人確診。美軍入伍事務司令部（USMEPCOM）最近一份備忘錄顯示，如果有武漢肺炎確診病史，將會終身禁止進入美軍服役，五角大廈已證實這項備忘錄的真實性。<br />\n<br />\n推特上最近流傳一份美軍入伍事務司令部的備忘錄顯示，「在面談或檢查期間，經實驗室檢查或臨床醫師診斷證實有武漢病毒病史者，將永久喪失（入伍）資格...」。<br />\n<br />\n《軍事時報》（Military Times） 報導，美軍入伍事務司令部在備忘錄中提到，有武漢病毒病史者將被標記為「不合格」，永久喪失入伍資格。美國國防部發言人麥克斯威爾（Jessica Maxwell）表示，這份備忘錄是真的，但她拒絕解釋詳細原因。<br />\n<br />\n《新聞週刊》（Newsweek） 分析，美軍這項禁令可能是源自武漢肺炎得有限研究，因為病毒對肺部和身體其他部位持久性傷害的資訊尚未明確，且病毒是否會在康復者重新復發，以及先前感染的人是否對病毒更具免疫力或更容易再感染病毒，這些問題都有待釐清。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3157691\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3157691&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=a7c46965\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3157691&h=10969c12\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3157691</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EXMcgS1UYAAGBp7?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEXMcgS1UYAAGBp7%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=01ae92d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.militarytimes.com/news/your-military/2020/05/06/coronavirus-survivors-banned-from-joining-the-military/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.militarytimes.com%2Fnews%2Fyour-military%2F2020%2F05%2F06%2Fcoronavirus-survivors-banned-from-joining-the-military%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=9cdffc7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.militarytimes.com/news/your-military/2020/05/06/coronavirus-survivors-banned-from-joining-the-military/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b42b22c7ef6c93872656843b2018a27498bc757","tid":2005281,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:22:07.000Z","msg":"呢隻病毒好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14962477574843d803029485a85c88ad7a61a9a8","tid":2005281,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67831035d3c76eb8d6d27ce7c0062d4419cb601","tid":2005281,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:24:28.000Z","msg":"長期番發...."},{"pid":"ed912b10db747699d9547119ecd533fc85b1b584","tid":2005281,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:24:41.000Z","msg":"訓練一個士兵起碼三四年時間<br />\n<br />\n美國今次真係好傷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bef83dbb35d29aac17da9bbfe9c14f7cf37c51","tid":2005281,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:24:44.000Z","msg":"強制退伍"},{"pid":"ed86617f456b3c69f6a0ac66fa2a5db621c0208f","tid":2005281,"uid":311611,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:33:21.000Z","msg":"正, 唔會無拉拉比人draft 去打中國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}